'''Red Threxa''' was a [[Suiraon]] who owned a [[Red Threxa's Boarding House|boarding house]] in [[Gelgelar Free Port/Legends|Gelgelar Free Port]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Gelgelar/Legends|Gelgelar]]. He was a quiet keeper of the house who left his clients alone to do what they wanted, provided they paid their rent.

